.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.TH plan 1  "plan " 
.SH NAME
plan \- Emit schema\-only context safe to paste into an AI agent prompt
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBmurk agent plan\fR [\fB\-\-tag\fR] [\fB\-\-json\fR] [\fB\-o\fR|\fB\-\-output\fR] [\fB\-\-vault\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Emit schema\-only context safe to paste into an AI agent prompt
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-tag\fR \fI<TAG>\fR
Filter by tag (repeatable)
.TP
\fB\-\-json\fR
Output as JSON
.TP
\fB\-o\fR, \fB\-\-output\fR \fI<OUTPUT>\fR
Output file (prints to stdout if omitted)
.TP
\fB\-\-vault\fR \fI<VAULT>\fR [default: .murk]
Vault filename
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
